Class LocalWeather

  • java.lang.Object
    • LocalWeather

  • public class LocalWeather
extends java.lang.Object
    The LocalWeather class stores the current forecast information. Used by the GUI, its instances are created by the Location class
    Author:
    David Newell, David Langford
